;
M. burgessi Schlabach, Donaldson, Hobelman, Miller & Lowman, 2018
;
M. eurystomum Maucci, 1991
(emended by
Morek et al. 2020a
);
M. longiungue Tumanov, 2006
;
M. minutum Pilato & Lisi, 2016
;
M. pseudotardigradum Surmacz, Morek & Michalczyk, 2019
